author: Associated Press
title: Trump says 'Noone knew healthcare could be so complicated' | Daily Mail Online
text: 'Nobody knew health care could be so complicated,' says Trump as he meets governors who fear Obamcare crisis - and is ridiculed by Democrats for his 'gaffe' Trump offered surprising analysis during summit with dozens of governors Many have expressed concern over impact of Republican determination to repeal and replace the Affordable Care Act Governors were warned at the weekend in report by management consultants that reform could leave them with less cash for Medicaid Democratic minority leader Nancy Pelosi said of Trump's statement: 'Nobody knew? No. He didn't know.' Published: 16:53 GMT, 27 February 2017 | Updated: 03:00 GMT, 28 February 2017 41 shares
